body:
**Minecraft, of course, has various structures, but there are not enough of those micro-details that could upgrade the world with (perhaps obvious) new buildings in the game, which would simply make it better. Therefore, I have distributed this data pack for versions of the game.**

The first version will contain a list that adds or revises new structures (Advanced World: Adventure & Explore v.1): 

- Swamp Hut
 (Revise: House of Witch and cats);

- Wandering House
 (Add: House of Wandering Trader and llamas);

- Air Ballons
 (Add: Red, Purple, White, Brown  Air Balloons);

- Cursed Tower
 (Add: Just debris tower with traps);

- End Debris and Small End Debris
 (Add: Just debris);

- Shipwrecks
 (Add: Pirate, Village Shipwrecks and Flying Dutchman);

- The Biggest Oak Tree
 (Add: Big oak tree);

- The Rock Garden
 (Add: Decoration for World);

- Villages
 (Revise: New Town Centers).

The second version will contain a list all previous structures and adds or revises new structures (Advanced World: Adventure & Explore v.2):

- Suspicious House
 (Add: Abandon house);

- The Biggest Oak Tree with bees
 (Revise: Big oak tree with bees);

- Jungle Village
 (Add: New Village);

- Mangrove Village
 (Add: New Village).
